{"title":"幼儿园的承包","authors":["余系中"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":6,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼儿园的承包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"余系中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新来的小朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是挂着眼泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是带着哭声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你将他们接收下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把眼泪育成笑脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让哭声长成歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这也是承包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实这些并不新鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只是轻轻地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搂过那一片哭声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用微笑吻干每一滴泪珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后就唱起歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些比妈妈的《摇篮曲》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还好听的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后就讲起故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些比奶奶的“狼外婆”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还好听的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后就用小刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把苹果削成一朵朵花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让那些花瓣飞进每一张小嘴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让那些花香漫入每一张小嘴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些小嘴就长成一朵朵花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些花在你身边开放起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你心中的花也开放起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的舞姿比花还好看"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真象花丛中的一只蝴蝶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼泪不见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭声不见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声长大了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声长大了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把长大的笑声和歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵到学校"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把长大的希望和自豪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送进学校"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后又收下一批"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼泪和哭声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是承包"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}